This file contains a few links to the materials related to Clupatra, its algorithm, usage, use etc.

There are presentations about Clupatra and related packages, namely MarlinTrk and KalDet/KalTest

1. F. Gaede's and S. Aplin's presentations at International Workshop on Future Linear Colliders in Granada, Spain, September 2011
http://ilcagenda.linearcollider.org/conferenceOtherViews.py?view=standard&confId=5134
-> Clupatra: Clustering based pattern recognition in a TPC (F. Gaede)
-> ILD Tracking code (S. Aplin)

2. F. Gaede's presentation at CLIC Workshop at CERN in January-February 2013:
http://indico.cern.ch/conferenceTimeTable.py?confId=204269#20130128
-> ILD Tracking

3. Here is also the presentation by O. Volynets given at LCTPC WP meeting #172 about
the use of clupatra to the Test Beam data. The presentation contains several important
things/limitations you need to know about using Clupatra for TB data:

http://ilcagenda.linearcollider.org/conferenceDisplay.py?confId=6037  -> Clupatra Tracking for test beam data

